DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260308T123000
DTSTAMP:20260302T001719
CREATED:20260218T140829Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260219T165455Z
UID:10003871-1772969400-1772973000@www.unioncong.org
SUMMARY:Youth Led Second Hour: Pierce Switzer (Assembly Room)
DESCRIPTION:Join us after worship\, as 10th-grander Pierce Switzer and his co-creators screen and discuss the mindset and piece that won them Best Documentary Short Grand Prize at the 2025 Montclair Film Festival. It’s a topic teaser around local legacies of Passaic River pollution and remediation\, and what accountability looks like today–topics that Union has long engaged with. Come\, support our youth and build conditions for action.
URL:https://www.unioncong.org/event/youth-led-second-hour-assembly-room/
LOCATION:Assembly Room
CATEGORIES:All Church Events,All Events
ORGANIZER;CN="Union Congregational Event":MAILTO:contact@unioncong.org
END:VEVENT
